OL,3,CMan charged after bomb squad called to
OL,4,Cdeal with 'suspicious items'
OL,6,FA man has been charged with explosives
OL,7,Foffences after two "suspicious items"
OL,8,Fwere discovered outside two houses,
OL,9,Fforcing residents to evacuate their
OL,10,Fhomes.
OL,12,FMiguel Sanchez, 22, has been charged
OL,13,Fwith three counts of possession of an
OL,14,Fexplosive substance for unlawful
OL,15,Fpurpose.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
