OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1781356274
OL,3,CMan charged after bomb squad called to
OL,4,Cdeal with 'suspicious items'
OL,6,FThe charges follow a major emergency
OL,7,Fresponse which began shortly after
OL,8,F6.05pm on 6 June, after police were
OL,9,Fcalled to reports of a suspicious item
OL,10,Fin a front garden on Abram Close in
OL,11,FFallowfield, Manchester.
OL,13,FThe Explosive Ordnance Disposal (EOD)
OL,14,Fteam carried out an assessment and, as
OL,15,Fa precaution, officers advised
OL,16,Fresidents from around 20 nearby homes
OL,17,Fto evacuate.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
