PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1781356274
OL,3,CMan charged after bomb squad called to
OL,4,Cdeal with 'suspicious items'
OL,6,FLess than 24 hours later, as the
OL,7,Fpolice investigation continued into 7
OL,8,FJune, a second suspicious item was
OL,9,Fdiscovered outside a house on
OL,10,FRostherne Avenue at around 2.45pm.
OL,12,FSanchez, of Edward Sutcliffe Close,
OL,13,FFallowfield, is scheduled to appear
OL,14,Fbefore Manchester Magistrates' Court
OL,15,Fon 12 June.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/3
